<h1>SameDifference Help</h1>

<br>Each level, you will click on 3 cards that form a set.
<br>Cards each have 4 characteristics.
<br>The cards need to be all the same or all different for each characteristic.
<br>If two of the cards are the same color, the third must be the same color.
<br>All three must either be the same number, or all different numbers.
<br>The shading must be either all the same or all different.

	<table width="50%" valign="top">
	<tr valign="top">
	<td width="25%">
		<b>Colors</b><br>
			Red<br>
			Blue<br>
			Black
	</td>
	<td width="25%">
		<b>Shapes</b><br>
			Circles<br>
			Squares<br>
			Triangles
	</td>
	<td width="25%">
		<b>Shading</b><br>
			Solid<br>
			Empty<br>
			Dot in the middle
	</td>
	<td width="25%">
		<b>Number</b><br>
			1<br>
			2<br>
			3
	</td>
	</tr>
</table>


<br>Valid set: 1 green clear triangle, 2 green solid squares, 3 green dotted circles
<br>Valid set: 2 red solid circles, 2 green solid circles, 2 purple solid circles
<br>Valid set: 3 red clear triangle, 3 red clear squares, 3 red clear circles
